# Stray build/tool artifacts that have shown up alongside real source files
# in dashboard/src (vue-tsc debug dumps, stale compiled JS, Vite temp files).
# Never intentional — if one of these reappears, it's noise, not source.
# Broadened 2026-07-15 (CODE-AUDIT.md item #1) from four explicit filenames to
# a catch-all: dashboard/tsconfig.json now sets noEmit so these shouldn't be
# generated at all going forward, but this stays as a backstop, and covers
# dateBuckets.js which the old explicit list had missed (it got committed).
*.tsbuildinfo
vite.config.ts.timestamp-*.mjs
dashboard/src/**/*.js
